txt.en: The dark beings that fly to the summons of the Doom-speaker are terrifying in their own right, but next to their master they seem as harmless as children.
The Gurvand, mutated and corrupted by countless years in the deepest delvings of Khazad-d√ªm, is perilously strong, weakening only in the Rune-light in his chamber.
Defeat the leaders of the Nameless horrors within the Dark Delvings.
The Void-eater is a Nameless foe whose time in Moria is undocumented, for few have ever looked upon it and lived.
